TY  - JOUR
TI  - On a Class of Growth Models
AU  - Kemp, Murray C.
AU  - Thānh, Phḁm Chí
AB  - [Johansen's analysis [4] of a vintage-capital growth model is extended by exploring the implications of alternative assumptions about expectations, with special attention being devoted to the polar assumptions of zero and perfect forsight; by introducing an arbitrary number of sectors; and by investigating the distributional aspects of the model.]
